{"tid":1690176,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"罷工其中一個最大嘅好處：正式確立黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-11-03T07:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:34:46.000Z","uid":79575,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"852b05647cb8c7b8b7ebd18fff242f9617ccb986","tid":1690176,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"罷工其中一個最大嘅好處：正式確立黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n點解？ <br />\n<br />\n<ins>有罷工/ 容許員工彈性上班：永遠變成黃店，一生一世都要懲罰佢。<br />\n<br />\n唔俾員工罷工/ 對請假員工懲處：必須杯葛，永遠唔會幫襯。<br />\n</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家大家有共識建立黃色經濟圈，而黃色經濟圈初見成效，<br />\n係咪應該以罷工嚟最全面嘅推廣？<br />\n<br />\n咩藍扮黃，黃扮藍，全部一試就知真面目，罷一次工，就得到一份最準確嘅黃藍地圖。<br />\n<br />\n而家罷工開始醞釀，大家都知道罷一次工唔易，分分鐘要兩個星期個推廣同文宣，而家諗定，<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n十一月十八日罷工</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n就差唔多可以俾黃店一次過準備同表態。<br />\n<br />\n我自己一個推唔起個post ，希望認同嘅手足可以一齊推上熱門，俾更多人知道。"},{"pid":"dc4a0d3964635865d38082b17bcafcad2348a630","tid":1690176,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9e87d99692a20ecb436c69a88b21d02a6c7077aa","tid":1690176,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c1ea2a039c02175b33dee59b7f7a1d7c4b0c1b","tid":1690176,"uid":331810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"召喚[自由鳥]一人一願望FF下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690166</a>"},{"pid":"603e359804338abaf52c3f2a08f2fd316bdb055e","tid":1690176,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"好毒<br />\n<br />\n唔俾員工罷就係藍色<br />\n<br />\n社會實驗黎添啦"},{"pid":"241c5241e3c9d0b7a50bade86e5d69566df378aa","tid":1690176,"